Package org.neo4j.kernel.impl.api.index.stats

Class IndexStatisticsStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.kernel.lifecycle.LifecycleAdapter
      • org.neo4j.kernel.impl.api.index.stats.IndexStatisticsStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IndexStatisticsVisitor.Visitable, ConsistencyCheckable, Lifecycle
    public class IndexStatisticsStore
extends LifecycleAdapter
implements IndexStatisticsVisitor.Visitable, ConsistencyCheckable
    A simple store for keeping index statistics counts, like number of updates, index size, number of unique values a.s.o. These values aren't updated transactionally and so the data is just kept in memory and flushed to a GBPTree on every checkpoint. Neither reads, writes nor checkpoints block each other. The store is accessible after init() has been called.
